metadata.name: Bunny Apocalypse #1/111
metadata.description:
She is surrounded by multiple of zombie rabbits, symbolizing the multitude of desires and impulses. A metaphor for the internal struggles we all face through especially in our modern society. The vibrant colors and intricate details add depth and beauty.

8640 x 10800 px

==========

Tools used,  
- Clip Studio Paint  
- Blender
